    "body": "The proposed solution here creates up to num_aggregator non-aggregatable messages  per committee which would take up more attestation positions in each block. This would make it more costly to verify and reduce the optionality in a block proposer including missing attestations from previous slots. \r\n\r\nThinking about how we might use subnet validation conditions to prevent this attack",
